name: Is it stated?
statement: Input The first line contains an integer $$$t$$$ ($$$1 \leq t \leq 100$$$) — the number of testcases. The following $$$t$$$ lines each contain a string of length at most $$$100$$$ consisting of lowercase English letters. Output For each test case, output " YES " or " NO ", denoting the answer. Example Input 10 is it stated submit ac accepted wa wronganswer tle timelimitexceeded Output NO YES NO YES NO NO NO NO NO YES
